data.description: Stunning Atrium Ranch Home w/Lake Views loaded w/custom upgrades & so meticulously maintained you can move in & relax! This executive home features an open floor plan, cathedral ceilings, custom built-ins, gleaming hardwood floors, bayed windows, architectural details, a new kitchen & updated baths, & 28x20 3 car, finished, garage. Fully updated kitchen w/custom cabinetry, stainless appliances, Silestone counters, & center island. Arched entry foyer w/pillars welcome you home to the large, open great room w/tinted atrium windows, 12 ft cathedral ceilings & open space to dining room. Luxurious primary bedroom suite w/large walk in closet & full bath w/separate jetted tub, shower, & dual vanity. Finished lower level is as perfect as the main level w/custom architectural details, a HUGE rec room, den/game space, & wet bar w/enough space for 6 seats PLUS a workout room w/glass doors PLUS 4th bedroom w/full bath. Enjoy the outdoors with 2 patios, one off great room & one off breakfast room.
